outputs.output_descr: The objectives of the project are to facilitate and account for the access of goods and construction materials into the Gaza Strip for UNDP projects. In addition, to demonstrate that the imported materials are adequately used for the projects they were intended for. Besides, to strengthen UNDP access and monitoring capacity. Also, to support key rehabilitation activities which are underway. As well as to ensure transparency for the effective use of construction materials for better working relationships with associated parties and stakeholders.

project_descr: The principal goal of the Access Coordination and Monitoring Support to Gaza project is to facilitate and account for the entry materials used for UNDP/PAPP projects in Gaza in support of the recovery and reconstruction process.
